          "sourceFilename": "1848_minimum_distance_to_the_target_element.java",
          "code": "class Solution {\n\n  public int getMinDistance(int[] nums, int target, int start) {\n    int min = Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {\n      if (target == nums[i]) {\n        int local = Math.abs(i - start);\n        if (local < min) {\n          min = local;\n        } else {\n          break;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n    return min;\n  }\n}\n",
